767
00:38:53,601 --> 00:38:55,270
You know, I could've handled that myself.

768
00:38:55,353 --> 00:38:56,396
Yeah.

769
00:38:57,521 --> 00:38:58,522
Yeah.

770
00:38:59,564 --> 00:39:02,026
Yeah. Yeah.

771
00:39:02,109 --> 00:39:06,154
You know, my grandfather,
he had psychotic issues.

772
