and I made it better. I'm making a plan.

784
00:39:49,398 --> 00:39:50,774
Oh, it's about control?

785
00:39:50,857 --> 00:39:52,275
Yep. Yep.

786
00:40:05,411 --> 00:40:06,412
Oh.

787
00:40:17,004 --> 00:40:18,798
-So?
-Good news.

788
00:40:18,881 --> 00:40:21,424
-I talked to Frank, and basically...
-Actually, I talked to Frank.

789
00:40:21,507 --> 00:40:23,218
The point is, somebody talked to Frank.

790
00:40:23,301 --> 00:40:26,970
They then talked to Tom,
and then they talked to a guy way up top.

791
00:40:27,053 --> 00:40:28,722
-The big guy.
-Kevin.

792
00:40:29,222 --> 00:40:30,808
And you got approved for a plan.

793
00:40:30,891 --> 00:40:32,058
Anna, just say the plan.

794
00:40:32,141 --> 00:40:33,935
-Okay, sorry. So typic...
-So, typically here...

795
00:40:34,018 --> 00:40:35,227
Anna. You're Anna?

796
00:40:35,811 --> 00:40:36,979
-No.
-Okay.

797
00:40:37,521 --> 00:40:38,730
So typically when you get here,

798
00:40:38,813 --> 00:40:41,024
you get to pick eternity,
and that's it. Bing, bang, boom.

799
