823
00:41:31,857 --> 00:41:34,109
So, just…

824
00:41:36,028 --> 00:41:38,321
Flip a coin and decide who's going first.

825
00:41:38,404 --> 00:41:39,531
No.

826
00:41:39,614 --> 00:41:42,451
I will not stand for another man
