I remember the sky being bluer.

858
00:43:30,498 --> 00:43:31,498
Oh.

859
00:43:32,207 --> 00:43:33,427
Was it always that shade?

860
00:43:33,959 --> 00:43:35,085
Oh, yeah. Pretty much.

861
00:43:36,919 --> 00:43:38,296
