862
00:43:40,673 --> 00:43:41,674
Yep.

863
00:43:43,717 --> 00:43:44,718
They move.

864
00:43:54,934 --> 00:43:56,478
Is it how you imagined it?

865
00:43:57,145 --> 00:43:58,229
It's perfect.

866
00:44:03,567 --> 00:44:05,361
Oh, boy. Oh. Okay.

867
00:44:06,402 --> 00:44:07,654
Okay.

868
00:44:10,615 --> 00:44:11,616
Can't die twice.

869
00:44:12,116 --> 00:44:13,492
You can't die twice.

870
00:44:13,575 --> 00:44:14,577
Okay.

871
