00:45:24,551 --> 00:45:26,928
I don't know why she fell in love with me.

893
00:45:27,011 --> 00:45:28,012
Mmm.

894
00:45:28,805 --> 00:45:32,474
Well, you're gonna have
to figure that out. And fast.

895
