-Joan.

925
00:47:28,613 --> 00:47:33,450
I would just sit and watch and wait.

926
00:47:37,870 --> 00:47:38,871
So I…

927
00:47:41,373 --> 00:47:43,124
I did wait for you, Luke.

928
00:47:46,544 --> 00:47:48,712
Yeah.

929
00:47:53,967 --> 00:47:54,968
Hmm.

930
00:47:55,051 --> 00:47:56,052
Hey.

931
00:47:58,179 --> 00:47:59,179
Come with me.

932
