940
00:48:47,219 --> 00:48:49,013
Remember, the exhibits aren't real.

941
00:48:49,096 --> 00:48:52,390
We take no responsibility
for emotional trauma.

942
00:48:52,473 --> 00:48:53,474
Happy reliving.

943
00:48:54,809 --> 00:48:55,811
You ready?

944
00:48:55,894 --> 00:48:56,895
