952
00:49:39,013 --> 00:49:40,180
Yeah.

953
00:49:40,263 --> 00:49:41,682
What's your name?

954
00:49:41,765 --> 00:49:44,142
-Luke.
-Nice to meet you, Luke.

955
00:49:45,226 --> 00:49:46,978
