980
00:52:21,230 --> 00:52:23,024
Can we just go please?

981
00:52:23,107 --> 00:52:24,526
Please…

982
00:52:24,609 --> 00:52:26,235
Oh, God, Luke. Please.

983
00:52:30,822 --> 00:52:32,490
Will you marry me?

984
00:52:32,573 --> 00:52:35,326
Of course.

985
00:52:35,409 --> 00:52:38,495
